Desc: Type 1 mechanism can not be blocked, but it can trigger the state changing of type 2 mechanism. To do so, enter the mechanism to be triggered in the Target ID. It has to stop on the mechanism to trigger it.
Type 2 mechanism is triggered by Type 1, and controlled by DefaultBlock, where, 1 is blocked by default, 0 is not blocked by default
After the player passes it, type 3 mechanism will convert from pass into block
